        crm:P3_has_note               "Real-time and historical data from the Digital Twin are visualised through the ARTEMIS IoT Viewer dashboard. The operation supports multiple user roles: curators and managers access real-time data and alerts; conservators analyse environmental stability and assess potential degradation risks; technical personnel monitor system performance. The operation correlates current sensor readings with past monitoring campaigns to support predictive conservation analytics. It also ingests the output of test scenarios (environmental fluctuation response, degradation suppression, vandalism detection, Digital Twin synchronisation verification)." ;
